structure.unit: ARTICLE LVI. MIAMI-DADE COUNTY CITIZENS TASK FORCE ON INCORPORATION

text.section:
Sec. 2-651. Creation; composition.
There is hereby created a Miami-Dade County Citizens Task Force on incorporation consisting of thirteen (13) members, one (1) member to be appointed by each County Commissioner. The task force shall remain in existence until September 30, 1994.
